    <item>
      <title>美联储柯林斯：CPI不是转折点，需要耐心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-12/fed-s-collins-cpi-not-a-turning-point-patience-needed-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿联邦储备银行行长苏珊·柯林斯表示，3 月份通胀数据处于预期的高端，但这并没有改变她认为通胀将继续下降的观点。她在彭博电视台接受了迈克·麦基的采访。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-12/fed-s-collins-cpi-not-a-turning-point-patience-needed-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 13:29:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东紧张局势刺激避险需求，国债飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/treasuries-surge-as-middle-east-tension-stokes-demand-for-havens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东战争的预期升级刺激了对避险资产的需求，美国国债周五大幅上涨，将收益率从今年迄今的高点拉低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/treasuries-surge-as-middle-east-tension-stokes-demand-for-havens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:58:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着公司和消费者借贷狂欢，花旗利润大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/citi-profit-beats-as-companies-consumers-go-on-borrowing-binge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着企业开拓融资市场以及消费者依赖信用卡，花旗集团的利润超过了分析师的预期——有迹象表明，长期加息将使大银行受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/citi-profit-beats-as-companies-consumers-go-on-borrowing-binge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:09:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>储户压力增大，富国银行 NII 未达预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/wells-fargo-sees-nii-drop-as-pressure-from-depositors-mounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国银行公司第一季度净利息收入未达到预期，这表明贷款增长放缓和支付更多存款的压力加大，正在侵蚀利率上升的好处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/wells-fargo-sees-nii-drop-as-pressure-from-depositors-mounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 11:01:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
